title: Sweet Dummies
description:
Casey and Danielle are together again, but are they really? As Casey tells the story of separating herself from the "chaff" on a wild trip they took to Miami. Plus, the ladies have turned a corner on Teresa and Luis, and want to stay in their love bubble too. Also there's a bear. 

Mark your calendars as Casey and Danielle are doing another Bitch Sesh Live (from home) show Thursday May 12th 5:30pm PST/8:30 EST to talk about the debut of the new season of Beverly Hills and more!! With special guests Jerry O'Connell, Brian Moylan plus surprises. Get your tix here https://app.loopedlive.com/c/3827
